Place 1/2 cup each pineapple and papaya, 1/4 cup mango, and one peeled banana in blender container. Add rice vinegar, honey and allspice; blend until smooth. Season to taste with salt and pepper. Place remaining pineapple, papaya and mango, plus kiwi fruit and strawberries in a large bowl. Slice remaining banana; add to bowl along with onion and mint. Pour about 1/2 cup vinaigrette over fruit; toss gently to coat.